<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/7e59f4f8-eca6-44d4-a7d1-57a7d89d5a92> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__36178.
_:b0__36178 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
