<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c2623bbe4720923ed43241ca8d57eaac>.
<#c2623bbe4720923ed43241ca8d57eaac> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bfd7a05ffaa780d972b604cf04854a3d>;
