<https://doi.org/10.5878/002901> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__5163.
_:b0__5163 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/89de22733d879189f44ac0b722481494>;
