<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5d9e2ca7a7020932ac94ae794083a211>.
<#5d9e2ca7a7020932ac94ae794083a211> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002935>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-09T06:33:27.689Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#5d9e2ca7a7020932ac94ae794083a211> {
