<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#965299f19eec360c0c381480555482b0>.
<#965299f19eec360c0c381480555482b0> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://www.geodata.se/resources/df439ba5-014e-44ec-86cb-ddb9e5ba306c>;
